# Draft:The 2nd Romanian Revolution

The 2nd Romanian revolution was initiated at first by prominent figure Arnaut Albert as he proclaimed himself Supreme Ruler and Dictator of Romania on the 23rd of July 2009.
He couped the Romanian government with help from the CNF (Californian Nationalist Front) led by Prominent figure in the United States Timoteo 'the new Nazi'. Timoteo sent lend lease to Arnaut. Furthermore Arnaut A. would make speeches in Bucharest saying: „Comuniști încă domnesc în România!” TRANSLATION: "The Communists still rule in Romania!" and he gained a lot of popularity with his speeches.
Furthermore in the Summer of 2009 he would initiate a coup overthrowing unpopular President Traian Băsescu as Arnaut would establish a ''''Legionary Dictatorship'.'''
